com.flyingspaniel.ranges

Interface Ranges.Comparable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of ranges that this range may be compared to (usually it's own class)
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Condition, Forecast, TimeInterval
    Enclosing class:
    Ranges

    public static interface Ranges.Comparable<T>
    Similar to java.utilComparable. Implement this interface if the range itself can do the comparison. The result returned should be one of the Ranges.Comparison constants below
